{"type": "article", "id": 10288, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-06-02T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8238, "name": "墨镜"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 1705, "name": "腕表"}, {"id": 1771, "name": "自行车架"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235417Zz1lIDHKbAsdqV36.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tSlash Lamp by Dragos Motica\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这是罗马尼亚设计师 Dragos Motica 推出的一款混凝土灯饰，而你拿到它之后，可以自行决定要不要“砸”掉，创造出属于你自己的独一无二的新灯饰。灯饰采用的是圆柱形状，铁丝网外面包裹着混凝土，顶部为木质。购买灯饰还将会获得一块石头，用来砸开混凝土，获得你的专属灯饰。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102301Aivqoc6WB1NLIGRh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102301tm6iGJN9YVK2dZD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102301YsQP1nlEFou2MrCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023029nRGxfjmoA5w7Mth.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102302HPDawZ62QMqNkUVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102303gu8wiC5HVIQryNpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102303kgqSiCY01mBP4sjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102304Kgu8fGsM9vwJzBCX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tJames by Linde Hermans\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">比利时设计师 Linde Hermans 最近推出了一个叫做 “James 管家”的系列产品，取“管家”是因为产品的设计试图把旧时管家的角色承担起来。一个扫帚作为整个产品的底座，扫帚把手变形后一个作为衣架，同时还承担着边桌的作用，看上去就像一个边打扫卫生边接过衣物的管家一样。这是<a href=\"http://www.lindehermans.be/james.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Linde Hermans 的主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023044sDYlw3vfEPeB21q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50694444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102304Ppx6sW2cA5FGXqEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50692042\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102305z4mZGWSyLiNqaMeh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48355263\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102305NQTYvJ6dPGBy1OKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50553506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102306LPsReGCxBUhF8YpE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102306W9omlIXpaBZHC2Vb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51440329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tShampoo by Shu Uemura\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">日本彩妆品牌 Shu Uemura 每年都在世界各地和艺术家合作推出联名系列，今年他们和三位来自澳洲的艺术家联合推出了限量版的洗发水系列，三位艺术家分别是，时装设计师 Emma Mulholland，插画家 Andrew Archer 和纹身艺术家 Dean Carlyle，他们为 Shu Uemura 的洗发水外面上加入了丰富多彩的包装，把洗发水变成了艺术品。目前售价约 346 元人民币，将于本月正式发售。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210230670wGl9drAhkIeuob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023076ieAHX9BPZnG8ry1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tBlack Matte Mirror by RETROSUPERFUTURE \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">意大利眼镜品牌 RETROSUPERFUTURE 最近推出了 2015 春夏 Black Matte Mirror 系列墨镜，在材料上均选用的是黑色磨砂，搭配镜面效果的 “Tri-alps” 镜片，时尚感十足，目前该系列有四个款式上的选择，售价在 149 到 229 欧元之间，<a href=\"http://retrosuperfuture.com/default/collections/super-black-matte-mirror.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102307MWVGpYDsz2lI4OEZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102307RmZar0AjSlpbqP28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023081Bu6J0vwSjr7Yq5G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102308hiHb4FTCKaB8fqNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tBike Shelves by Vadolibero\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">意大利设计公司 Vadolibero 致力于在全世界推广自行车文化，他们最近推出了一款自行车架，专门为喜欢木工的骑行者设计。木架采用立式结构，带有多个单元格子抽屉，既能存放自行车，又能对不同的物品进行归类收纳，甚至连存放钥匙，眼镜等小物品的地方都被分门别类设计。而顶层托盘则可以满足充电需求。<a href=\"http://vadolibero.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是官方主页</a>，点击可以查看更多详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102308hMyxrIY8FNQGAv6u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102309C8UxSZd9lrIP4Rws.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102309kfqSbYx8iFtvKEno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102310N6YrmtHTRc1VK9gM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023103VRB2eOcsSQhIJlK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023110LHwVKRgymejfSNi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102311HDA3wLKPjXSzIiMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102312ojMa7cRzHWECgVZP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021023124QFzmVSWJTB8kv5R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102313L9c1QIN2lCVvDtw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tISSEY MIYAKE “V” by Tokujin Yoshioka\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这是日本设计师 Tokujin Yoshioka 为 ISSEY MIYAKE 推出的一款全新的 “V” 表，其最大的特色在于表带利用不锈钢的挤出成型技术打造出不同的 V 型凹槽，从而从不同的角度都可以反射出光芒，看上去十分美丽。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102313AKovPuQqc7IgW4f2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102313I1Gt9gO2WYHksn7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102314Xmw3MngkDhvEOtyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102314eRSCQ1z4YWvOtksu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102315ZzmbtK7leB2ovRuI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68229167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\n\n"}